sequenceDiagram
  participant Client
  participant Csrf as StatelessCsrfFilter
  participant SecurityConfig
  participant Mapper as RoleAuthorizationAuthorityMapper
  participant TenantFilter as HttpTenantFilter
  participant Resolver as TenantResolver
  participant TenantService
  participant Controller
  Client->>Csrf: HTTP request with optional CSRF header and cookie
  Csrf->>SecurityConfig: continue when allowed or token matches
  SecurityConfig->>SecurityConfig: validate JWT issuer
  SecurityConfig->>Mapper: map Keycloak roles to local grants
  alt multitenancy enabled
    SecurityConfig->>TenantFilter: continue request
    TenantFilter->>Resolver: resolve tenant
    Resolver->>Resolver: read tenantId header or subdomain
    Resolver->>TenantService: lookup tenant when needed
    Resolver-->>TenantFilter: tenant id
  end
  SecurityConfig->>Controller: authorize URL and method
